89
00:11:07,133 --> 00:11:09,800
But I think, okay, I will explain it later to wrap up.

90
00:11:10,500 --> 00:11:14,966
I think that there is a dimension of reflexive thinking,

91
00:11:15,433 --> 00:11:25,100
which remains a domain of philosophy, I'm more of a philosopher here, in which for structural reasons cannot be covered up by science,

92
00:11:25,533 --> 00:11:30,700
and point two on this, I would especially like to insist,

93
00:11:31,500 --> 00:11:35,700
we should be very careful about what do we mean by belief.

94
